    participant G as Game
    participant B as Board

    M->>G: start_game(Health_Agent)

    G->>AI: get_move(Health_Scan)
    AI->>U: get_valid_moves(Health_Record)
    U->>B: get_piece(Health_Agent)
    AI->>G: make_move(Health_Scan)
    G->>B: set_piece(Health_Sync)
    G->>B: is_valid_move(Health_Record)
    B->>P1: get_pieces(Health_Sync)
    B->>P2: get_pieces(Health_Scan)
    G->>B: get_captured_pieces(Health_Agent)
    B->>P1: set_pieces(Health_Vault)
    B->>P2: set_pieces(Health_Vault)
    G->>B: is_game_over(Health_Vault)
    G->>B: get_winner(Health_Record)
